('foundation', 'tenses-advanced', 'intermediate', 'He _____ reading that book for weeks.', '["has read", "has been reading", "is reading", "read"]', 1, 'Present perfect continuous: has been + V-ing. Extended duration "for weeks".', 'easy'),
